explanation: "| **Condition** | **Organism** |\n| --------- | -------- |\n| Donovanosis | **Klebsiella granulomatis** |\n| Oroya fever | **Bartonella bacilliformis** |\n| Rat bite fever | **Streptobacillus moniliformis** |\n| Pinta | **Treponema carateum** |",
