tags: ["ZVRecommended", "PYQ", "INI-CET May 2024"],
text: "Match the following:",
options: [{"id": "A", "text": "a-2, b-1, c-4, d-3", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "B", "text": "a-3, b-1, c-4, d-2", "is_correct": true}, {"id": "C", "text": "a-2, b-4, c-1, d-3", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "D", "text": "a-1, b-2, c-3, d-4", "is_correct": false}],
explanation: "<br><br>| **Virus** | **Genome Type** | **Key Feature** |\n| ----- | ----------- | ----------- |\n| **Rotavirus** | dsRNA | Reoviridae family |\n| **SARS-CoV-2** | ssRNA | Coronavirus, positive-sense RNA |\n| **Parvovirus** | ssDNA | Smallest DNA virus |\n| **HPV** | dsDNA | Papillomavirus causing warts & cancer |",
