subcategory: "09-general-microbiology-sterilisation",
tags: ["ZVRecommended", "PYQ", "INI-CET May 2025"],
text: "A patient underwent cardiac surgery and was admitted to the ICU. He later developed ventilator-associated pneumonia and was started on empirical antibiotics. A few hours later, the patient developed acute kidney injury (AKI). Serum procalcitonin was sent. Which of the following statements regarding procalcitonin is correct?",
