tags: [],
text: "A chronic smoker with persistent cough was found to have a lung mass on imaging. A bronchoscope was used to obtain a lung biopsy. Based on the Spaulding classification, what category does this medical device fall under, and  what is the appropriate sterilisation or disinfection agent?",
