explanation: "| **Treatment Component** | **Details** |\n| ------------------- | ------- |\n| **DOC for uncomplicated gonorrhoea** | Third-generation cephalosporins; treat both partners |\n| **Ceftriaxone** | 250 mg IM, single dose |\n| **Cefixime** | 400 mg orally, single dose |\n| **If coexisting Chlamydia** | Add azithromycin or doxycycline |",
